Gayatri Sadhana, benefits of the Gayatri Sadhana and why it's important to have a practice. I will be presenting a standing form of this Gayatri Sadhana on December 17th with Vivia Astraia followed by her Dynamic Mudra Flow and pot luck . See you there :)
Margie should we reschedule movie to sunday?
I'll be walking on fire that night and jumping into frozen streams with Wisconsin tribe.  Everyone else show up.... it'll be wonderful & magical!  I'll astro travel and we'll be together.  Love You!
